Plays a state.
This could be used to synchronize your animation with audio or synchronize an Animator over the network.
@param stateName The name of the state the will be played.
@param layer The layer where the state is.
@param normalizedTime The normalized time at which the state will play.
@param stateNameHash The  hash of the state.